## üß† Key Takeaways
- **Infrastructure is Priority:** 2025 was about buying "hard assets"‚Äîrailways, data centers, and energy grids.
- **Valuations Recovered:** The public-private valuation gap has narrowed as private equity marked up assets in a lower-rate environment.
- **AI Utility Phase:** M&A has shifted from model-building to data-handling and cybersecurity.

